FDateField.calendar({

  bool enabled,
  void Function(DateTime?)? onSaved,
  void Function()? onReset,
  AutovalidateMode autovalidateMode,
  String? forceErrorText,
  Widget Function(BuildContext, String) errorBuilder,
  Key? key,
})
